      • fromRootEntropy

        @NonNull
public static AccountKey fromRootEntropy(@NonNull
                                                  byte[] rootEntropy,
                                                  @NonNull
                                                  android.net.Uri fogReportUri,
                                                  @NonNull
                                                  String fogReportId,
                                                  @NonNull
                                                  byte[] fogAuthoritySpki)
        AccountKey static constructor for root entropy with fog info
        Parameters:
        rootEntropy - 32 bytes of randomness. It is used to derive account keys therefore it must be treated as highly sensitive information.
        fogReportUri - URL of the fog report server including port (i.e. fog://fog-ingest.test.mobilecoin.com:443)
        fogAuthoritySpki - fog authority public key a byte array, provided by the fog operator
        fogReportId - The fog report server may serve multiple reports, this id disambiguates which one to use when sending to this account
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the fogReportUri is invalid
